[{"id":"FT561585","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<p>The four pictures present a story. Imagine you are writing the story to a friend. Narrate a complete story as suggested by the pictures. Give your story a beginning, a middle, and an end.&nbsp;Type your response in the target language.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Picture 1 shows a group of people, including children and adults, gathering around an older woman in the center of a room. The old woman is sitting at a table with a cake with candles on it. There are balloons in the background of the room and some nicely wrapped gifts on a smaller table next to the table with the cake. Everyone is happy and smiling.Picture 2 shows a young man in a T-shirt outside of a house knocking on a door.He is looking through the window and watching the festive decoration and the celebration taking place inside. Above the manâ€™s head is a thought bubble containing an image of a wrapped gift, a question mark, and an exclamation point.Picture 3 shows another man, wearing a suit, walking toward the house. He is holding a huge bouquet of flowers in his hands. Seeing the man in the suit approaching with flowers, the same young man in a T-shirt shows his arms outstretched and looks relieved.Picture 4 shows a young woman opening the door from inside the house. The same man in the suit and the same young man in the T-shirt enter the house through the door smiling. Both men now hold some flowers in their hands. The flower bouquet held by the man in the suit now appears visibly smaller compared to his bouquet in picture 3.\" height=\"376\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/media.academicmerit.com/41e47d4e4f361aab0738ee6975873d78/original.png\" width=\"355\" /></p>\n"}]